    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<h1>sadaka ya ushirika</h1><h2>Uhalisia:</h2><p>Kwenye Agano la Kale, &quot;sadaka ya ushirika&quot; ilikuwa aina ya dhabihu iliyotolewa kwa sababu mbalimbali, kama vile kutoa shukrani kwa Mungu au kutimiza nadhiri.</p><ul><li><p>Dhabihu hii ilihusisha mnyama ambaye angeweza kuwa wa kiume au wa kike. Hii ilikuwa tofauti na dhabihu ya kuteketezwa, ambayo ilihitaji mnyama wa kiume pekee.</p></li><li><p>Baada ya kutoa sehemu ya dhabihu kwa Mungu, mtu aliyetoa sadaka ya ushirika aligawana nyama na makuhani pamoja na Waisraeli wengine.</p></li><li><p>Kulikuwa na mlo uliotolewa pamoja na sadaka hii ambao ulijumuisha mkate usiotiwa chachu.</p></li><li><p>Hii mara nyingine huitwa &quot;sadaka ya Amani.&quot;</p></li></ul><p>(Tazama pia: <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"25560\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">sadaka ya kuteketezwa</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"25761\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">kutimiza</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"25802\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">sadaka ya nafaka</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"25807\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">sadaka ya hatia</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"26081\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">sadaka ya amani</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"26121\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">kuhani</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"26188\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">dhabihu</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"26328\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">mkate usiotiwa chachu</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"UnfoldingWord_TranslatorWords_vow\" data-resourceType=\"UWTranslationWords\">nadhiri</span>)</p><h2>Marejeleo ya Biblia:</h2><ul><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:25-1Chr21:27\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 21:25–27</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:35\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 29:35</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:5-Exod24:6\">Kutoka 24:5–6</a></p></li><li><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev3:3-Lev3:5\">Walawi 3:3–5</a></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num6:13-Num6:15\">Hesabu 6:13–15</a></p></li></ul><h2>Data ya Neno:</h2><ul><li><p>Strong&apos;s: H8002</p></li></ul>",
